<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.6.2">
<l>nillāta peruveḷḷam neṭuvicumpiṉ mītōṭi nimirntakālam</l>
<l>mallāṇṭa taṭakkaiyāl pakiraṇṭa makappaṭutta kālattaṉ</l>
<l>ṟellāru maṟiyārō vemperumā ṉuṇṭumiḻnta vecciltēvar</l>
<l>allātār tāmuḷarē yavaṉaruḷē yulakāva taṟiyīrkaḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Doesn’t everyone know of the time that day when the great unstoppable flood</l>
<l rend="indent">expanded, spreading above the vast heavens,</l>
<l>The time then when the outer firmament was entrapped by his broad hands</l>
<l rend="indent">that [once] overpowered the wrestlers?</l>
<l>Are there deities who were not spittle that our lord ate up and spewed out?</l>
<l>Understand that the world comes to be only by his grace.</l> 
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
